{"tid":2498670,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"香港嘅教育內卷化問題","createTime":"2021-04-21T10:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T14:35:42.000Z","uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e0cba88ae57f8b4629b32c60b0c86610b01f12ed","tid":2498670,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:18:04.000Z","msg":"喺香港出世只要屋企有番咁上下經濟能力，就會送仔女去學唔同嘅興趣同補習班，但係大家嘅仔女都越學越多嘢之後，其實就會將條平均線不斷推高<br />\n<br />\n最終小朋友壓力越嚟越大越嚟越辛苦，學曬所有父母要佢學嘅嘢之後先發現自己只係處於起跑線，出到社會之後，大部分之前學嘅所謂技能其實都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n大家都喺同一條起跑線上面競爭，但係正式起步之前大家都被迫無意義地跑圈熱身，係正式開始比賽之前可能要先跑兩圈做熱身，慢慢變成三圈四圈....<br />\n<br />\n相反歐美就更加在於培養仔女嘅興趣，之後沾著投資喺仔女嘅興趣上面，令到每個細路仔嘅技能都唔一樣，大家都可以喺自己嘅跑道上面努力，而每一條路都可以活出精彩嘅人生"},{"pid":"03622ad1e474c13764a136c8ee5b3d6419e9b909","tid":2498670,"uid":77968,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:24:28.000Z","msg":"你同我講無用<br />\n你同班新移民講先有用"},{"pid":"8e450a9ec3d5a86eddb3603d6b3da0af7f84e6f9","tid":2498670,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:26:44.000Z","msg":"内你老母<br />\n陰啲陰啲推蝗語<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冚家鏟五毛+鍾共打手<br />\n<br />\n李宇軒擺明已經做咗金手指 仲有咁多人幫佢辯護<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gPAayT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gPAayT</a><br />\n#2 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n連登培生培心會員討論區（1）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2476780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2476780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"30e3c6c3c3b757485c5373aeeb09d286d779f242","tid":2498670,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:27:31.000Z","msg":"廢話-.-唔係咩叫內卷?人口越黎越多+資本壟斷+吸血越黎越嚴重+生產技術無突破,何止教育,全世界發達國家各方面都內卷緊"},{"pid":"a033f73e2d716718bf197773c36bcf9d9bd05085","tid":2498670,"uid":391580,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8e450a9ec3d5a86eddb3603d6b3da0af7f84e6f9","tid":2498670,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:26:44.000Z","msg":"内你老母<br />\n陰啲陰啲推蝗語<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冚家鏟五毛+鍾共打手<br />\n<br />\n李宇軒擺明已經做咗金手指 仲有咁多人幫佢辯護<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gPAayT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gPAayT</a><br />\n#2 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n連登培生培心會員討論區（1）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2476780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2476780</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"內卷係蝗語？<br />\n<br />\n冇文化嘅弱智仔"},{"pid":"08016aabbaa239afca7d7b682f33aee50502c56e","tid":2498670,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"內卷化（英語：Involution）是一個社會學概念，也翻譯為過密化，用以形容社會文化因為重複勞作、發展遲緩。 內卷化出自拉丁語詞彙「involutum」，原意是「轉或捲起來」，因德國哲學家伊曼努爾&middot;康德、美國人類學家亞歷山大&middot;戈登威澤、美國社會學家克利福德&middot;格爾茨等人的使用而聞名。"},{"pid":"ef62fd3650322ad806946ada00e3d109d2de1b5a","tid":2498670,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sixthtone.com/news/1006391/how-one-obscure-word-captures-urban-chinas-unhappiness\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sixthtone.com%2Fnews%2F1006391%2Fhow-one-obscure-word-captures-urban-chinas-unhappiness&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dKpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=1ea63cff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sixthtone.com/news/1006391/how-one-obscure-word-captures-urban-chinas-unhappiness</a><br />\n<br />\n呢篇都幾有趣 <br />\nlihkg已經唔係一個可以容許quality discussion嘅地方<br />\n搵d風氣好d嘅地方討論，唔好浪費自己時間"},{"pid":"818c91ff6b76713c7aaaa8f578aadc4d241c154b","tid":2498670,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ef62fd3650322ad806946ada00e3d109d2de1b5a","tid":2498670,"uid":227172,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.sixthtone.com/news/1006391/how-one-obscure-word-captures-urban-chinas-unhappiness\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sixthtone.com%2Fnews%2F1006391%2Fhow-one-obscure-word-captures-urban-chinas-unhappiness&d=Hmcjt6v